headline: ConocoPhillips Strikes 20-Year LNG Deal With Sempra's Port Arthur
summary: COP secures a 20-year deal to buy 4 MTPA of LNG from Sempra's Port Arthur Phase 2, expanding its global energy footprint.

headline: Analysts Keep Raising ConocoPhillips Target Prices - Shorting Puts is a Good Play Here
summary: ConocoPhillips' stock has risen since the Aug. 7 release of its Q2 results. Analysts have been upping their price targets. COP stock looks undervalued based on its historical yield. Shorting out-of-the-money puts is a good play.
